<div id="contBotLeft" class="dynamicTextCtnr">
<div id="openingText">
<h2>Custom Wedding Invitations and Fine Stationery</h2>
<p>January and February have traditionally been very strong months for happy couples seeking wedding invitations to celebrate their May or June wedding.  Members of the Stationers Guild congratulate them and encourage them to gain some valuable planning advice and see samples of custom wedding invitations by visiting our <a href="http://www.stationersguild.org/weddings.html" target="_blank">custom wedding invitations page.</a></p>
<p>Also, the first quarter of each year are traditionally "slow" months for many printing companies.  As such, they generally offer some exceptional promotions for fine stationery and custom invitations.  To learn more about current promotional offers visit Guild members stores in your neighborhood that sell <a href="http://www.stationersguild.org/stationery.html" target="_blank">fine stationery</a>, custom <a href="http://www.stationersguild.org/weddings.html" target="_blank">wedding invitations</a>, <a href="http://www.stationersguild.org/baby.html" target="_blank">baby announcements</a>, and invitations and announcements for all occasions.  In-house printing and calligraphy is offered in many of these stores.</p>
<p>These neighborhood stationers would like to share  their passion for fine papers and cordially invite you to visit their store and experience first-hand the differences in paper textures and weights, colors and printing processes that have enchanted countless generations.   With an almost limitless customization and paper options to choose from, Guild members are committed to work with you to design your stationery or special invitation.   Member stores have the experience, range of products and service quality to make your shopping experience more worthwhile.   Don’t sacrifice apparent convenience for expertise, service and quality. Whether you are looking for a wedding invitation, baby announcement, social stationery or casual invitation, seek out a member store in your neighborhood.</p>
<p>This website is dedicated to providing the consumer with relevant and current information on <a href="http://www.stationersguild.org/fine_papers.html" target="_blank">fine stationery and custom invitations</a>.   While there is much helpful information on the website, our Guild members strongly believe that selecting fine paperss is best done in person.  There is simply no way to adequately represent texture, color, paper weight and subtle differences in printing processes on the internet.    Why struggle with low-image screen resolutions and design options that tend to all look the same?  Qualified help may be just around the corner.  Appointments are recommended, so schedule your appointment now with one of our Guild members.</p>
</div>
</div><!-- end of contBotLeft -->

